	<div class="page-content">
				<div id="section-id-1504690873218" class="sppb-section " ><div class="sppb-row-overlay"></div><div class="sppb-container-inner"><div class="sppb-row"><div class="sppb-col-md-12" id="column-wrap-id-1504690873219"><div id="column-id-1504690873219" class="sppb-column" ><div class="sppb-column-addons"><div id="sppb-addon-1504769839932" class="clearfix" ><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-image-content aligment-right clearfix "><div style="background-image: url(../images/Demo/elements/about.jpg);" class="sppb-image-holder"></div><div class="sppb-container"><div class="sppb-row"><div class="sppb-col-sm-6"><div class="sppb-content-holder"><h3 class="sppb-image-content-title">Hello!</h3>
				<p class="sppb-image-content-text">	We at Milky produce organic dairy products - cow and goat milk, bulgarian yogurt, greek yogurt, yogurt drinks, butter and grass-fed organic ghee, hard cheese selection, gauda, ementaler, yellow cheese and white cheese.<br />Our products are created by best traditional recipes and all certificated organic. <br /><br />
				Our cows and goats live for 10 months in the Paithal Mountains, when the weather is warm and we take exceptional care for our animals.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><section id="section-id-1504769839937" class="sppb-section " ><div class="sppb-row-overlay"></div><div class="sppb-row-container"><div class="sppb-row"><div class="sppb-col-md-4" id="column-wrap-id-1504769839938"><div id="column-id-1504769839938" class="sppb-column" ><div class="sppb-column-addons"><div id="sppb-addon-1504769839943" class="clearfix" ><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-feature sppb-text-left "><div class="sppb-addon-content sppb-text-center"><div class="sppb-media"><div class="pull-left"><span class="sppb-img-container"><img class="sppb-img-responsive" src="../images/Demo/elements/organic.png" alt="100% Organic"></span></div><div class="sppb-media-body"><div class="sppb-media-content"><h4 class="sppb-addon-title sppb-feature-box-title sppb-media-heading">100% Organic</h4><div class="sppb-addon-text">	Our products are labeled as &ldquo;100% organic&rdquo; and contain only organically produced ingredients and processing aids, excluding water and salt. No other ingredients or additives are permitted.</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sppb-col-md-4" id="column-wrap-id-1504769839939"><div id="column-id-1504769839939" class="sppb-column" ><div class="sppb-column-addons"><div id="sppb-addon-1504769839973" class="clearfix" ><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-feature sppb-text-left "><div class="sppb-addon-content sppb-text-center"><div class="sppb-media"><div class="pull-left"><span class="sppb-img-container"><img class="sppb-img-responsive" src="../images/Demo/elements/products.png" alt="Variety of Products"></span></div><div class="sppb-media-body"><div class="sppb-media-content"><h4 class="sppb-addon-title sppb-feature-box-title sppb-media-heading">Variety of Products</h4><div class="sppb-addon-text">	A dairy product is food produced from the milk of mammals. We produce cow and goat milk, yogurt, butter, buttermilk, ghee, hard cheese, white cheese, feta, ementaler, halloumi cheese.</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sppb-col-md-4" id="column-wrap-id-1504769839940"><div id="column-id-1504769839940" class="sppb-column" ><div class="sppb-column-addons"><div id="sppb-addon-1504769839978" class="clearfix" ><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-feature sppb-text-left "><div class="sppb-addon-content sppb-text-center"><div class="sppb-media"><div class="pull-left"><span class="sppb-img-container"><img class="sppb-img-responsive" src="../images/Demo/elements/bulgaricus.png" alt="Lactobacillus Bulgaricus"></span></div><div class="sppb-media-body"><div class="sppb-media-content"><h4 class="sppb-addon-title sppb-feature-box-title sppb-media-heading">Lactobacillus Bulgaricus</h4><div class="sppb-addon-text">	This is is one of several bacteria used for the production of yogurt.First identified in 1905 by the Bulgarian doctor Stamen Grigorov, the bacterium feeds on lactose to produce lactic acid, which is used to preserve milk.</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-id-1504769839987" class="sppb-section " ><div class="sppb-row-overlay"></div><div class="sppb-row-container"><div class="sppb-row"><div class="sppb-col-md-12" id="column-wrap-id-1504769839988"><div id="column-id-1504769839988" class="sppb-column" ><div class="sppb-column-addons"><div id="sppb-addon-1504769839995" class="clearfix" ><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-header butter sppb-text-center"><h3 class="sppb-addon-title">Our Team</h3></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sppb-col-md-3" id="column-wrap-id-1504769839989"><div id="column-id-1504769839989" class="sppb-column" ><div class="sppb-column-addons"><div id="sppb-addon-1504769840003" class="clearfix" ><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-person sppb-text-left  "><div class="sppb-addon-content"><div class="sppb-person-image"><img class="sppb-img-responsive" src="../images/Demo/elements/team1.png" alt="Ivan Stefanov"></div>
				<div class="sppb-person-information">Savior<span class="sppb-person-designation">Chairman</span></div>
				<div class="sppb-person-introtext">He was a jockey and he love horses. We met him on a convention and we offered him a position at our company. He is with us since and is very happy.</div><div class="sppb-person-social-icons"><ul class="sppb-person-social"><li><a target="_blank" href="http://www.facebook.com/"><i class="fa fa-facebook"></i></a></li><li><a target="_blank" href="http://twitter.com/"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i></a></li><li><a target="_blank" href="http://plus.google.com/"><i class="fa fa-google-plus"></i></a></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sppb-col-md-3" id="column-wrap-id-1504769839990"><div id="column-id-1504769839990" class="sppb-column" ><div class="sppb-column-addons"><div id="sppb-addon-1504769840014" class="clearfix" ><div class="sppb-addon sppb-addon-person sppb-text-left  "><div class="sppb-addon-content"><div class="sppb-person-image"><img class="sppb-img-responsive" src="../images/Demo/elements/team2.png" alt="Maria Petrova"></div>
				<div class="sppb-person-information"><span class="sppb-person-name">Maria </span><span class="sppb-person-designation">Manager Animal Care</span></div>
